data.description: NEVER FLOODED Like NEW! Charming Huge 2 story home, beautiful BIG private HEATED swimming POOL and SPA, SOLAR SYSTEM installed 2023, extreme 2021 UPDATE/UPGRADE KITCHEN, BATHS, ROOF, GARAGE DOORS and OPENERS with/WiFi connectivity, Amazing rare 2 find BEST award winning schools, High ceiling throughout ,PRICE TO SELL FAST due to the seller is moving back to CA, Marble, WOOD/TILE,100% SOLID WOOD KITCHEN, GRANITE,+stainless appliances+Fridge+BIG farm sink INSTANT HOT WATER 4 baby food, tea, coffee,4 Zone A/C W/DEHUMIDIFIER, LED/CFL save $, design wrought iron staircase, Game-RM+4 big bed Rooms, 2nd MASTER overlooking BIG POOL+fruit trees+separate office/Man-Cave in backyard, Close to Shopping, Schools and More! Definitely a must see! For immediate interest, please contact the listing agent.
